<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Reset Your Password - {{appName}}</title>
    <style>
      /* Basic styling - Keep it simple and use inline styles for critical elements if needed */
      body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 30px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #dddddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #0056b3; /* Consistent color */
      }
      p {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        background-color: #007bff; /* Use a primary color */
        color: #ffffff !important; /* Ensure text is white */
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .important-note {
        margin-top: 25px;
        padding: 15px;
        background-color: #fff3cd; /* Light yellow for warning/info */
        border-left: 4px solid #ffeeba;
        color: #856404; /* Darker text for contrast */
        font-size: 0.95em;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #666666;
        border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
        padding-top: 15px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>

      <p>Hi,</p>

      <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account associated
        with
        <strong>Rental</strong>.</p>

      <p>If you made this request, please click the button below to set a new
        password. If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email â€“
        your password will remain unchanged.</p>

      <p style='text-align: center;'>
        <a href='{{url}}' class='button'>Reset Your Password</a>
      </p>

      <p>If you're having trouble clicking the "Reset Your Password" button,
        copy and paste the following URL into your web browser:</p>
      <p><a href='{{url}}'>{{url}}</a></p>

      <div class='important-note'>
        <strong>Didn't request this change?</strong>
        If you didn't ask to reset your password, please ignore this email. No
        changes will be made to your account, and your current password is still
        secure. Do not forward this email or share the link.
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        <p>Thank you,<br />
          The Rental Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>